{"tid":614672,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"［DSE］其實背補習句考英文作文係咪真係work？","createTime":"2018-04-02T17:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T12:33:33.000Z","uid":136553,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a97044abaf6185d41bf9b355a6eb9a0637e46cdb","tid":614672,"uid":136553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:22:06.000Z","msg":"平時補習果啲notes<br />\n剩係望下個結構點寫，要包啲咩<br />\n比我果啲罐頭句，難字，真係望都無望過<br />\n我覺得成件事好虧，可能用無翻啲句，或者自己根本唔識點用<br />\n用翻自己文字寫<br />\n但見啲同學個個走去背<br />\n有啲驚"},{"pid":"fca2c3cb01b865813e4e91f23ea2b4f9321eaa79","tid":614672,"uid":30836,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:22:36.000Z","msg":"睇你點定義work"},{"pid":"6142f8cda1f2a0c18b2bc7682decc9f442fa4569","tid":614672,"uid":136553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a97044abaf6185d41bf9b355a6eb9a0637e46cdb","tid":614672,"uid":136553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:22:06.000Z","msg":"平時補習果啲notes<br />\n剩係望下個結構點寫，要包啲咩<br />\n比我果啲罐頭句，難字，真係望都無望過<br />\n我覺得成件事好虧，可能用無翻啲句，或者自己根本唔識點用<br />\n用翻自己文字寫<br />\n但見啲同學個個走去背<br />\n有啲驚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:22:45.000Z","msg":"用<span style=\"color: red;\">唔</span>翻"},{"pid":"b58854527857e1af82832c7929dfafbf42c8fa27","tid":614672,"uid":136553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fca2c3cb01b865813e4e91f23ea2b4f9321eaa79","tid":614672,"uid":30836,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:22:36.000Z","msg":"睇你點定義work"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:23:43.000Z","msg":"level 5以上<br />\n平時學校寫文都有，<br />\n不過從來無用過補習句"},{"pid":"37331aafb92f5923074b9188be322bf40b83320a","tid":614672,"uid":72228,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:23:50.000Z","msg":"比得你背比得你溫都唔撚去溫<br />\n你係咪寫得出比佢更靚更簡單嘅英文先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d24c832b3c2044d46f5f87c8ffe98c2f42c27f1","tid":614672,"uid":80,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:24:09.000Z","msg":"有用<br />\n<br />\n學點寫都重要 唔需要特別用深字"},{"pid":"ed99f977a3775962aee5887e3cc1e61dcd82db55","tid":614672,"uid":136039,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:28:25.000Z","msg":"唔work咁教你來做乜？"},{"pid":"cfab44e27bba58a0e8ce67ed851b370704488cfb","tid":614672,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b58854527857e1af82832c7929dfafbf42c8fa27","tid":614672,"uid":136553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fca2c3cb01b865813e4e91f23ea2b4f9321eaa79","tid":614672,"uid":30836,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:22:36.000Z","msg":"睇你點定義work"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:23:43.000Z","msg":"level 5以上<br />\n平時學校寫文都有，<br />\n不過從來無用過補習句"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:33:21.000Z","msg":"咁要用得好靈活<br />\n一生硬就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有作文又唔係淨係講你用咗幾多complex sentence㗎嘛 好難一概而論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇多啲 讀多啲點都有好處嘅"},{"pid":"16c9598226f6b766be6dc9c546d6900a41aa4dfe","tid":614672,"uid":30762,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"37331aafb92f5923074b9188be322bf40b83320a","tid":614672,"uid":72228,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:23:50.000Z","msg":"比得你背比得你溫都唔撚去溫<br />\n你係咪寫得出比佢更靚更簡單嘅英文先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:34:45.000Z","msg":"下<br />\n簡單？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你打開d 補習notes睇下<br />\n一堆垃圾句子故作玄虛<br />\n左加右加慌死唔夠長咁<br />\n複雜到鬼佬都唔明"},{"pid":"5c921282bfa66fd2ea3f5f2e2375f98ec0c01f56","tid":614672,"uid":48362,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:35:17.000Z","msg":"內容 推論過程 grammar&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;靚字句"},{"pid":"88ddbd71625c4f07dad285cf012846e0011c5a78","tid":614672,"uid":136553,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c921282bfa66fd2ea3f5f2e2375f98ec0c01f56","tid":614672,"uid":48362,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:35:17.000Z","msg":"內容 推論過程 grammar&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;靚字句"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:45:06.000Z","msg":"我都係咁認為<br />\n都唔知點解啲人會走去背句"},{"pid":"536064cc2a3bb8b5cac486ddf9d215423f98115b","tid":614672,"uid":161352,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T18:16:12.000Z","msg":"差既背黎可以寫多兩句<br />\n例如背左it is a must for us就憑空elab多句啦<br />\n<br />\n勁既可以衝雙21（一般5**18.7就夠）<br />\n<br />\n當然要用得正確先有用"},{"pid":"f000b2e2d54c4ca1b221a3b1505fc50525fee428","tid":614672,"uid":47801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T18:26:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35b03a909fa26b4ec1436296817bc77a8584af27","tid":614672,"uid":125441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c921282bfa66fd2ea3f5f2e2375f98ec0c01f56","tid":614672,"uid":48362,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T17:35:17.000Z","msg":"內容 推論過程 grammar&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;靚字句"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T05:20:38.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  當年作開lv3 到最後1個月狂煲marc wong d文/grammer既練習就沖左4最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實作文有d位都要學下點表達,可能姐係你所講既背 不過背字個人覺得無咩用 好多時都用唔反/或者唔岩語境. 學點樣表達果個approach 反而中更重要&lt;-好多用果種flow都會用某幾隻字去講，用果個structure表達就更加寫得好睇"},{"pid":"6416c423eae37443745b7e3f1c336afad42d2843","tid":614672,"uid":76587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T06:02:55.000Z","msg":"老土啲講句<br />\n真係睇你係咪融匯貫通到<br />\n就咁背幾句落去會好突兀"},{"pid":"b57e391091d2828407c225f04c59abc286e7b8bb","tid":614672,"uid":173589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T06:12:13.000Z","msg":"Grammar 最緊要，d難字唔熟用法(睇example sentence)就唔好用<br />\ngrammar冇錯又貼題一定有4"},{"pid":"766a0740a26ccc4c683415aea0d7f22789093b0e","tid":614672,"uid":37358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T07:23:22.000Z","msg":"你本身有lv5 or above嘅，背返啲勁嘅句子無壞嘅<br />\n但你lv3/4 就唔好啦，弄巧反拙！"},{"pid":"7045fc8bcda26afdfd1b4c8b36e871cd182a29bf","tid":614672,"uid":122183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T16:13:37.000Z","msg":"我覺得DSE英文作文致勝之道在於你有冇能力去靈活運用字句，而唔係鬥難鬥深鬥生僻，為用而用咁生搬硬套往往只會係反效果。所以我認為你唔需要太在意人地背得多唔多，最重要係要用嘅時候用得出用得啱，quality over quantity!<br />\n<br />\n利申 15DSE 英文作文5** 冇補過任何所謂名師"},{"pid":"94dfe1dd4252df49771eee2b6751b2f35ae9ddce","tid":614672,"uid":160579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T16:49:12.000Z","msg":"dse用melody tam啲百搭phrase去寫partB<br />\n15/21<br />\n<br />\n不過用自己文字寫嗰篇就21/21<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n表達自然最緊要"},{"pid":"111fa9c71758ab7d0d1286f757903b636b6bfc6d","tid":614672,"uid":12754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T00:05:17.000Z","msg":"背文背到拎滿分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n詳情youtube search Kris Lau"},{"pid":"2b595c20cceff7f6ad22dff03b9233764e766a2d","tid":614672,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"111fa9c71758ab7d0d1286f757903b636b6bfc6d","tid":614672,"uid":12754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T00:05:17.000Z","msg":"背文背到拎滿分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n詳情youtube search Kris Lau"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T00:06:21.000Z","msg":"利申<br />\n上埋youtube <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1316e024b95cf03b99c7304a2bbfddfcd4f33350","tid":614672,"uid":143915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"111fa9c71758ab7d0d1286f757903b636b6bfc6d","tid":614672,"uid":12754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T00:05:17.000Z","msg":"背文背到拎滿分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n詳情youtube search Kris Lau"},"citedBy":0,"rep